<i>- Sarah.
-Felix.</i>

01:36.720 --> 01:38.324
<i>My phone is gonna die, just listen.</i>

01:38.400 --> 01:39.765
Okay, yeah, I'm listening.

01:39.920 --> 01:42.730
Ferdinand took Kira and Mrs S.

01:43.040 --> 01:44.849
<i>- What?
- Go check the safe house.</i>

01:45.120 --> 01:47.282
It's all Rachel,
she's taken over from Susan.

01:47.760 --> 01:49.888
(SIGHS) Are you okay?

01:52.240 --> 01:53.366
Yeah, I'm fine.

01:53.480 --> 01:56.051
<i>FELIX: No, you're not. You're lying.
I can hear it in your voice.</i>

01:56.120 --> 01:58.327
Look, it doesn't matter, okay?

01:58.440 --> 02:01.364
Okay, Rachel took the cure
before Cosima could get to it.

02:01.440 --> 02:02.771
- What's happening?
-just, Sarah,

02:02.840 --> 02:04.968
get your ass off the island.

02:06.760 --> 02:08.649
I'm not leaving without Cosima.

02:08.919 --> 02:11.321
<i>- Put me on speaker.
{SXGHS}</i>

02:11.400 --> 02:15.007
<i>Ira, Susan said she sent Cosima
to a boat. Where is that?</i>

02:15.080 --> 02:17.208
- Is Susan all right?
-Answer the question.

02:17.280 --> 02:20.090
On the west side of the island,
there is a boathouse.

02:20.160 --> 02:23.289
<i>It's at a river mouth
downstream from the village, but...</i>

02:23.360 --> 02:25.089
Downstream from what village?

02:26.200 --> 02:27.326
Hello?

02:29.840 --> 02:30.921
Ira.

02:31.880 --> 02:33.245
What village?

02:54.240 --> 02:56.242
(WHISPERS) Come on, come on.

02:58.160 --> 02:59.286
Shit.

03:10.520 --> 03:11.885
Sorry, monkey.

03:18.000 --> 03:19.764
Please, please, please, please.

03:21.640 --> 03:23.369
Yes! Yeah.

03:24.240 --> 03:26.811
Thank you. Thank you. Thank you.

03:36.640 --> 03:37.641
(GRUNTS)

