KIRA: <i>Mummy?</i>

04:04.120 --> 04:05.565
Mummy, wake up.

04:06.000 --> 04:07.206
Come on.

04:08.000 --> 04:09.729
<i>There's so much to do today.</i>

04:10.200 --> 04:11.201
Wake up, Mummy.

04:11.600 --> 04:13.250
<i>- Wake up!</i>
- <i>Ki</i> ra .

