Hello?

04:26.720 --> 04:27.881
(BIRDS CHIRPING)

04:36.320 --> 04:37.321
Who's there?

04:48.080 --> 04:49.286
(GRUNTING)

04:50.040 --> 04:51.485
-(GROANING)
-(GRUNTING)

04:52.200 --> 04:53.247
(YELLING)

