Look at me.

06:15.000 --> 06:17.731
<i>Have you finished your homework?
Can you please excuse us?</i>

06:17.800 --> 06:19.404
<i>I'm breaking in.
I'm gonna keep you warm.</i>

06:19.480 --> 06:21.642
<i>MESSENGER:
You won't be allowed to stay with her.</i>

