20:17.560 --> 20:20.450
What do you do with furs
that still smell like fur?

20:20.520 --> 20:22.090
- Don't move.
-Oh!

20:22.480 --> 20:23.641
(SCREAMS) Let go of me!

20:24.360 --> 20:25.885
(SCREAMING)

20:26.320 --> 20:27.446
Donnie!

20:27.520 --> 20:30.251
Donnie! Donnie! Donnie!

20:31.440 --> 20:33.329
Let go! Let go of me!

20:53.280 --> 20:55.123
- It needn't be so harsh.
-Shit!

20:55.920 --> 20:56.967
FELIX: Hello.

20:58.200 --> 20:59.440
Which faction are you from?

20:59.520 --> 21:01.010
My name is Mr Frontenac.

21:01.600 --> 21:04.001
There is only one faction now.

21:04.600 --> 21:05.601
Oh.

21:06.120 --> 21:07.167
Consolidation.

21:07.760 --> 21:09.808
The bane of diversity, if I may say.

21:09.880 --> 21:11.723
Particularly under dear Rachel.

21:11.800 --> 21:14.644
You needn't fear the change upon you.

21:15.040 --> 21:17.520
Rachel has taken
a special interest in your family.

21:17.640 --> 21:18.641
Yeah.

21:19.320 --> 21:20.526
I can see that.

21:24.000 --> 21:25.001
(SIGHS)

21:25.600 --> 21:28.251
Shall you and I do this amicably?

21:38.960 --> 21:41.406
Budgy fudgers! I can't breathe.

21:42.680 --> 21:44.967
Alison, stay calm.

21:46.320 --> 21:47.765
Where are Donnie and Helena?

21:48.240 --> 21:49.571
How should I know?

21:49.800 --> 21:53.521
Helena was out murdering God's
creatures and my husband abandoned me.

21:53.600 --> 21:54.840
Where do you think they'd go?

21:55.840 --> 21:57.171
What is happening, Art?

21:58.240 --> 21:59.969
They want you to come in, Alison.

22:00.800 --> 22:02.370
Your sisters, your family...

22:02.880 --> 22:03.927
They want a truce.

22:04.600 --> 22:05.601
A truce?

22:06.120 --> 22:08.600
Kidnapping children is
a Neo-definition of a truce?

22:08.680 --> 22:11.286
You need to understand
the benevolence on offer here.

22:11.600 --> 22:12.761
Comes from above.

22:13.120 --> 22:16.169
I'm sworn not to harm
a single hair on a single clone head.

22:17.280 --> 22:18.281
(GRUNTS)

22:18.360 --> 22:19.691
Oh, oh!

22:19.760 --> 22:20.841
- Now, where's is Helena?
-Er...

22:20.920 --> 22:22.331
- In the woods.
-What's her backup plan?

22:22.400 --> 22:23.731
I don't know her backup plan.

22:23.800 --> 22:25.450
- You do.
-No! No, I don't.

22:25.520 --> 22:27.727
She ran. Where does
she go when she runs?

22:28.840 --> 22:30.171
I don't know.

22:33.520 --> 22:35.682
Okay, I believe you.

22:36.360 --> 22:37.407
No harm.

22:38.160 --> 22:39.207
We good, Art? We done?

22:41.240 --> 22:42.844
We're just getting started, partner.

22:44.240 --> 22:45.651
Let's take you home and tuck you in.

22:45.920 --> 22:47.968
And maybe we'll all live
long, healthy lives.

22:50.000 --> 22:51.411
(DOORS SHUT)

23:19.520 --> 23:20.521
(GRUNTS)

23:24.960 --> 23:28.851
CHARLOTTE: "We are all Revival's
children chosen for a brighter future,

23:29.600 --> 23:32.046
"where our frail bodies
become so much stronger

23:32.280 --> 23:34.487
"and death and ageing
haunt us no longer."

23:35.040 --> 23:37.611
- This place is scary.
-Yeah.

23:39.160 --> 23:40.685
Do you know what a myth is?

23:41.480 --> 23:43.687
It's an old, old story,

23:43.760 --> 23:47.048
and some of it's true
and some of it is not.

23:47.800 --> 23:50.690
But it's told to us
to teach us something.

23:50.880 --> 23:51.881
(DOOR OPENS)

23:56.120 --> 23:58.202
- Delphine.
-I'm so sorry.

24:00.640 --> 24:03.689
- I thought you were dead.
-I wasn't allowed to contact you.

24:05.440 --> 24:09.047
- Why are you here now?
-Please listen, there is no time.

24:12.200 --> 24:14.282
- Transport is waiting.
-Could you give us 10 minutes?

24:14.360 --> 24:15.771
- What's going on?
-Please.

24:17.320 --> 24:18.810
This isn't what I want either.

24:19.040 --> 24:20.326
Where are you taking her?

24:20.880 --> 24:22.325
She has a research trip.

24:23.400 --> 24:24.890
I'm going to Sardinia.

24:26.400 --> 24:27.526
Sardinia?

24:28.200 --> 24:29.645
We each have a role here,

24:30.600 --> 24:31.761
Cosima.

24:38.760 --> 24:41.081
I don't understand,
this place is insane.

24:41.160 --> 24:44.369
What, you were saved
by a 170-year-old man?

24:44.440 --> 24:46.204
The science is real. Cosima, you...

24:46.280 --> 24:48.806
In here, you can't make
the obvious assumptions.

24:48.880 --> 24:50.564
It's like nothing I've seen before.

24:56.600 --> 24:58.125
You didn't think it would be there?

24:59.800 --> 25:00.801
(SIGHS)

25:02.600 --> 25:04.489
I need something to hold on to.

25:06.240 --> 25:09.881
This entire island
is a decades-long pro-longevity study.

25:11.520 --> 25:14.251
- And everyone here is participating?
-Yes.

25:14.720 --> 25:15.960
Stem-cell therapy,

25:16.040 --> 25:17.485
cryonics, caloric restriction,

25:17.560 --> 25:19.562
immunotherapy, cloning...

25:19.640 --> 25:21.051
I mean, think about it.

25:21.240 --> 25:23.846
If you want to genetically
improve the human race,

25:24.920 --> 25:26.763
life extension is the first principle.

25:27.560 --> 25:28.721
This place...

25:29.400 --> 25:31.368
This is the heart of Neolution.

25:34.080 --> 25:36.481
There is a child, and she has cancer.

25:36.560 --> 25:39.564
I've seen others like her brought here
for some experimental treatment.

25:39.640 --> 25:40.721
What does this have to do with...

25:40.800 --> 25:42.529
Rachel is ramping up their agenda.

25:43.400 --> 25:45.050
And this has something to do with it.

25:45.240 --> 25:46.844
(KNOCKING) It's time.

25:48.840 --> 25:53.129
There's a clinic across the camp
with a red cross on the door.

25:53.760 --> 25:55.205
This is the key. Okay?

25:56.240 --> 25:58.049
Come on, let's go.

25:58.880 --> 26:01.850
(WHISPERS) I hid your treatment
in the back of a fridge.

26:02.560 --> 26:03.607
It's ready.

26:04.000 --> 26:05.286
I'll find you and Charlotte.

26:05.600 --> 26:06.931
- Let's go.
-Okay?

26:12.520 --> 26:13.965
Follow the crazy science.

26:28.360 --> 26:29.725
(DOOR SHUTS)

26:29.880 --> 26:31.211
(GRUNTS)

26:39.080 --> 26:40.241
(DOGS BARKING)

26:44.720 --> 26:46.210
They're scenting her this way.

26:46.320 --> 26:47.810
So what are you waiting for?

26:49.120 --> 26:50.770
Who's hanging game way out here?

26:53.800 --> 26:56.201
Just track the girl down.
That's what he wants.

26:56.320 --> 26:57.560
Move it, Amar.

26:58.440 --> 26:59.930
(DOGS BARKING)

27:20.640 --> 27:21.721
(GROAN5)

27:36.760 --> 27:37.761
KIRA: <i>Mummy.</i>

27:38.360 --> 27:40.044
<i>- Mummy, wake up.
-(GROANS)</i>

27:40.480 --> 27:41.481
<i>Mummy!</i>

27:56.240 --> 27:57.446
(DOGS BARKING)

28:12.160 --> 28:13.764
Cooper, what the hell
is going on out here?

28:16.880 --> 28:18.325
Could it have been the girl?

28:20.200 --> 28:21.247
Mmm-mmm.

28:21.320 --> 28:23.721
- Then what was it?
-Must have been a bear.

28:24.040 --> 28:25.041
(BARKING)

28:26.560 --> 28:28.130
AMAR: Wasn't a bear,
something stabbed it.

28:28.280 --> 28:29.361
It was a bear.

28:30.760 --> 28:31.886
You got that?

28:33.640 --> 28:35.961
It's gonna be dark soon.
Let's cut and head back.

28:36.080 --> 28:37.241
What about the girl?

28:39.720 --> 28:40.960
Good luck to her.

29:18.200 --> 29:19.326
Hello.

29:21.960 --> 29:23.803
Do you want to be left alone?

29:24.800 --> 29:26.529
It's a complicated question.

29:28.040 --> 29:29.041
I know.

29:31.320 --> 29:32.765
I'm sorry about your friend.

29:34.720 --> 29:35.881
Yeah, well...

29:36.800 --> 29:39.565
Never really had any, erm,
real control over it.

29:41.160 --> 29:42.491
(MUSIC IN BACKGROUN D)

29:42.560 --> 29:44.005
Wow. Wow, it's time.

29:44.080 --> 29:45.411
- What?
-It's time!

29:45.760 --> 29:47.603
(SONG PLAYING OVER SPEAKERS)

29:56.520 --> 29:57.965
What is going on?

30:00.200 --> 30:01.611
P.T. has something to tell us.

30:02.400 --> 30:03.447
COSIMA: What?

30:05.360 --> 30:06.771
(PEOPLE CHATTING)

30:09.080 --> 30:10.411
(ALL CHEERING)

30:17.800 --> 30:18.801
(SIGHS)

30:18.920 --> 30:19.921
Thank you.

30:21.920 --> 30:24.127
I am humbled to

30:24.200 --> 30:28.250
have pierced the veil and to address you
on behalf of Mr Westmorland.

30:28.880 --> 30:31.451
Like you, I was selected.

30:33.120 --> 30:38.001
I know now his hand
guided my entire life.

30:39.120 --> 30:42.442
I know, Susan Duncan, my mother,

30:43.360 --> 30:45.124
once stood here as I am.

30:45.840 --> 30:48.571
Appointed to move the future forward,

30:49.360 --> 30:50.486
and she did.

30:52.480 --> 30:53.925
She created me.

30:54.800 --> 30:57.804
It is time to be brave, to sacrifice.

30:58.240 --> 31:01.050
The fruits of nearly 200 years

31:01.120 --> 31:04.488
of Neolution science
are now within our grasp.

31:05.160 --> 31:06.969
And we, here,

31:07.440 --> 31:09.488
shall drink from the fountain first.

31:09.560 --> 31:10.846
(ALL CHEERING)

31:38.120 --> 31:39.201
(CAR LOCK CHIRPS)

31:45.240 --> 31:46.446
- Freeze.
-Whoa!

31:46.520 --> 31:48.170
On your knees, hands on your head.

31:48.240 --> 31:49.685
Okay, just calm down.

31:50.800 --> 31:51.847
Oh, Jesus!

31:51.920 --> 31:52.921
(BOTH GRUNTING)

31:54.600 --> 31:55.886
(CHOKING)

32:05.600 --> 32:07.011
-(GRUNTS)
-(HELENA GROANS)

32:07.440 --> 32:08.487
Helena. Helena!

32:08.560 --> 32:09.561
Ouch!

32:10.000 --> 32:11.047
Oh, my God!

32:13.560 --> 32:16.245
- Stick in baby.
-Okay. Okay. just...

32:16.760 --> 32:17.886
Oh, my God.

32:17.960 --> 32:19.450
We're gonna get you
to the hospital, okay?

32:20.040 --> 32:21.121
This is gonna hurt.

32:21.360 --> 32:22.771
-(SCREAMS)
-Oh, God!

32:29.200 --> 32:30.201
(DOOR OPENS)

32:51.320 --> 32:52.321
(GAS PS)

33:42.240 --> 33:43.446
Oh, my God!

33:44.080 --> 33:46.367
- Shh... Shh... It's me. It's me.
-Sarah?

33:47.040 --> 33:49.361
- Wait... What?
-I came to get you.

33:49.520 --> 33:50.681
How did you get here?

33:52.080 --> 33:53.081
Oh, my God!

33:53.560 --> 33:54.721
You're bleeding.

33:55.840 --> 33:57.649
- Hold on.
-There's a boathouse...

33:57.840 --> 33:59.365
- Found a boat.
-Sit.

33:59.440 --> 34:00.487
Sit down.

34:01.360 --> 34:02.930
What the hell happened?

34:03.960 --> 34:05.405
Rachel went mad.

34:05.880 --> 34:07.803
-(SIGHS)
-Yea h, I know.

34:08.440 --> 34:10.806
- Just, here. Let me take a look at you.
-(GROANS)

34:19.960 --> 34:21.324
Mmm. (GASPS)

34:21.400 --> 34:24.529
Er, what? Erm, I'm sorry. I...
I didn't fall asleep.

34:27.239 --> 34:28.525
What about your cure?

34:30.120 --> 34:32.521
Er... Well, Rachel didn't get all of it.

34:33.199 --> 34:34.725
You're meant to put that in your uterus?

34:35.360 --> 34:36.850
I was kind of hoping
you would, actually.

34:37.639 --> 34:39.449
No. No way. You and I
are gonna go find Charlotte...

34:39.800 --> 34:40.847
(SIGHS)

34:40.920 --> 34:42.570
...and we're gonna get you
to somewhere safe.

34:42.639 --> 34:43.721
We'll treat you there.

34:43.800 --> 34:46.929
Who gives a shit if the founder of
Neolution is still alive?

34:48.080 --> 34:49.161
I do.

34:49.880 --> 34:50.880
You're crazy.

34:51.280 --> 34:53.647
- We need to go, Cosima.
-No, I can't.

34:53.920 --> 34:55.001
What are you talking about?

34:55.960 --> 34:56.960
Look.

34:57.440 --> 34:58.771
Think about it, Sarah.

34:59.160 --> 35:01.731
Whatever this place is, it's the answer.

35:02.960 --> 35:04.041
I don't give a shit.

35:04.440 --> 35:07.523
I came all this way.
Rachel tried to kill me.

35:07.600 --> 35:09.489
Cosima, you're gonna come home with me.

35:09.560 --> 35:10.800
No. You need to go back.

35:11.120 --> 35:14.886
And take care of Siobhan and Kira,
and I need to stay here for us.

35:15.320 --> 35:17.243
We'll never be free if I leave now.

35:18.600 --> 35:20.250
- She's not here.
-What?

35:21.800 --> 35:23.086
(WHISTLES)

35:24.280 --> 35:25.645
(MAN SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY)

35:30.480 --> 35:32.528
This is gonna be for me. You have to go.

35:33.480 --> 35:34.527
Oh, Christ!

35:35.280 --> 35:36.805
I really don't want to leave you here.

35:37.920 --> 35:39.365
This Way's clear. Come on!

35:39.440 --> 35:41.283
There is something in the woods, Cosima.

35:42.000 --> 35:43.001
What?

35:43.160 --> 35:45.447
- What do you mean?
-I don't know. I don't know.

35:45.760 --> 35:48.047
It attacked me, all right?

35:49.400 --> 35:50.686
Just take care of yourself.

35:51.480 --> 35:54.484
- Find some answers.
-Yeah, yeah.

36:03.000 --> 36:04.650
(MEN SHOUTING)

36:10.920 --> 36:11.967
(SIGHS)

36:14.320 --> 36:15.731
(BREATHING DEEPLY)

36:22.760 --> 36:23.761
Oh!

36:23.960 --> 36:24.961
(DOOR OPENS)

36:25.840 --> 36:26.841
What are you doing?

36:28.080 --> 36:29.127
She's here.

36:30.360 --> 36:31.361
Oh.

36:32.200 --> 36:33.690
Leave us, please.

36:38.840 --> 36:42.162
Not the easiest procedure
to perform on oneself, is it?

36:45.640 --> 36:48.166
I knew some of
the sell line was missing.

36:48.760 --> 36:50.842
I keep very thorough logs.

36:52.120 --> 36:53.610
Stop, Cosima.

36:54.680 --> 36:56.045
You'll hurt yourself.

37:00.400 --> 37:01.686
Give me the needle.

37:03.960 --> 37:05.041
Cosima?

37:06.080 --> 37:08.287
I'm as invested in this as you are.

37:14.120 --> 37:15.246
Thank you.

37:18.520 --> 37:20.204
Come. Lie down.

37:23.400 --> 37:24.561
You're sure you know what you're doing?

37:27.360 --> 37:29.328
It has to be inserted
into the uterine wall.

37:29.400 --> 37:30.606
(SHUSHING)

37:31.160 --> 37:32.161
Relax.

37:33.440 --> 37:34.566
Just breathe.

37:45.000 --> 37:47.446
There's no need to be afraid any more.

37:48.240 --> 37:50.242
He wants you to be part of this.

37:52.560 --> 37:55.040
You and I are going to cure us all.

37:55.760 --> 37:57.125
Just hit me, Rachel.

38:28.600 --> 38:29.965
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

39:09.600 --> 39:10.601
Hey!

39:25.600 --> 39:26.601
Night, night.

39:46.840 --> 39:48.251
It's a new day, Sarah.

39:57.000 --> 39:58.001
Kira!

39:58.080 --> 40:00.890
- We'd like to study her here at...
-(CLANKING)

40:00.960 --> 40:01.961
We found MK.

40:02.040 --> 40:04.281
Rachel wants to restart human cloning.

40:04.360 --> 40:05.600
The easier you make this for us,

40:05.680 --> 40:07.808
the easier you make it
on my new partner here.

40:07.880 --> 40:09.041
My babies are special like Kira.

40:09.320 --> 40:10.731
They want our biologist.

40:10.800 --> 40:15.203
I know you created me, so what the hell
is the point of all of this?

40:15.280 --> 40:17.044
We're going to take
such good care of you.

40:17.160 --> 40:18.366
You bitch!
